## Projects

- saito-rust-workspace

		A cargo workspace containing all the rust projects. Workspace is used to easily share and link code.

- saito-core

		Core library which contains all the core logic for saito functionality.

- saito-rust

		This project contains rust code required to run the Rust node. This will run the core logic in a multithreaded environment.

- saito-wasm

		Contains the WASM interface which will be used by the saito-js library. This project will provide an interface of the core saito logic to be used by the js projects

- saito-js

		Contains the JavaScript library which handles IO related functionalities for the core logic layer (compiled into WASM)

- saito-web (To be copied from saito-lite-rust)

		Will contain the modules and other arcade functionalities.


## Components

Controllers are the main entry points for the core saito library. They will be receving all the events from other threads and call the necessary functions.

- Blockchain Controller
		Responsible for managing blockchain and mempool related actions
- Miner Controller
		Mines concurrently to the blockchain functions.
- Routing Controller
		Routes messages between threads and manages peers.


## Design Decisions

1. Common functionality to be implemented and maintained at a single place.
2. Components to function their specific responsibility only.
3. Ability to easily refactor the design and the code
4. Easily testable code
5. Library dependencies should be minimum and can be replaceable.
